<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <!-- Required meta tags -->
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-TX8t27EcRE3e/ihU7zmQxVncDAy5uIKz4rEkgIXeMed4M0jlfIDPvg6uqKI2xXr2" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/jquery.terminal/css/jquery.terminal.min.css"/>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
    <title>Monpoke Game</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="nav">
        <h3>Monpoke CLI Game</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="main">
        <div class="app__left">
            <div class="instructions">
                Welcome to Monpoke, a turn based battle system - where two teams face off against each other with their respective Monpoke! The games rules are as below:
                <ul>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        The game consists of 2 teams, each team has a variable number of Monpoké.
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        Each Monpoké has 2 attributes, HitPoints (HP) and Attack Power (AP). 
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        The 2 teams engage in a simple turn-based battle.                        
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        A team’s turn can be either choosing a Monpoké OR attacking with their currently chosen Monpoké.
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        Attacking Monpoké depletes the enemy Monpoké HP for the value of their AP.
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        A Monpoké is defeated when its HP is less than or equal to 0.
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        The game ends when all of a team’s Monpoké have been defeated.
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                To play the game, you have the following commands available to you:
                <ul>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        CREATE <team-id> <monpoké-id> <hp> <attack> -> to create a team
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        ICHOOSEYOU <monpoké-id> -> to select current Monpoke
                    </li>
                    <li class="app__instructions">
                        ATTACK -> attack opponent using your selected Monpoke
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <br>
                Good luck!

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="app__right" id = "terminal" >
        </div>
    </div>
